### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
### SupportGenie — Document Ingestion API Tests
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = sk_live_test_token_123

### ─── Health Check ──────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### ─── Upload PDF ────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/documents/upload-pdf
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./test.pdf
--boundary--

### ─── Add URL ───────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/documents/add-url
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Artificial_intelligence"
}

### ─── Add Text ──────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/documents/add-text
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Password Reset Guide",
  "text": "How to reset your password: Step 1 — Go to Settings. Step 2 — Click on 'Account Security'. Step 3 — Click 'Reset Password'. Step 4 — Enter your email address. Step 5 — Check your inbox for a reset link. Step 6 — Click the link and enter a new password. Your password must be at least 8 characters long and contain a mix of letters, numbers, and symbols. If you do not receive the email within 5 minutes, check your spam folder. For further assistance, contact support@cyclecorp.in."
}

### ─── Crawl Website (async — returns 202) ───────
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/documents/crawl-website
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://docs.example.com",
  "max_pages": 10,
  "max_depth": 3
}

### ─── Add YouTube Transcript ────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/documents/add-youtube
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ"
}

### ─── Poll Document Status ──────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/documents/status/REPLACE_WITH_DOCUMENT_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─── List Documents ────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/documents
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─── Delete Document (replace ID) ──────────────
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/documents/REPLACE_WITH_DOCUMENT_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─── Auth Failure — Missing Token ──────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/documents

### ─── Auth Failure — Invalid Token ──────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/documents
Authorization: Bearer sk_live_invalid_token
